---
// Services / Programs section with Bento Grid
---

<section id="services" class="section services">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">Nuestros Programas</h2>
            <p class="section-desc">Diseñados para elevar tu potencial.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bento-grid">
            <div class="bento-item bento-item--large">
                <div class="bento-content">
                    <h3>Alto Rendimiento</h3>
                    <p>Entrenamiento intensivo para competidores.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="arrow-link">→</a>
                </div>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530549387789-4c1017266635?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
                    alt="Swimming lanes" class="bento-bg">
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item">
                <div class="bento-content">
                    <h3>Clases Grupales</h3>
                    <p>Aprende y socializa en el agua.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bento-overlay"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item">
                <div class="bento-content">
                    <h3>Personal Trainer</h3>
                    <p>Atención 1 a 1 para perfeccionar tu técnica.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bento-overlay"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item bento-item--wide">
                <div class="bento-content">
                    <h3>Recuperación & Spa</h3>
                    <p>Relájate después del esfuerzo.</p>
                </div>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600965962102-9d260a3015b7?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
                    alt="Spa area" class="bento-bg">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.services {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
}

.bento-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    grid-auto-rows: 300px;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
    .bento-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        grid-auto-rows: 350px;
    }

    .bento-item--large {
        grid-column: span 2;
        grid-row: span 1;
    }

    .bento-item--wide {
        grid-column: span 3;
    }
}

.bento-item {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.bento-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

.bento-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
}

.bento-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
}

.bento-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.15;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
}

.bento-item:hover .bento-bg {
    opacity: 0.25;
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

.arrow-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
}
</style>
